OL,3,CNew rule approved to crack down on
OL,4,Csecond homes in national park
OL,6,FA controversial planning rule has been
OL,7,Fapproved in Eryri National Park in an
OL,8,Fattempt to crack down on second home
OL,9,Fownership.
OL,11,FThe 'Article 4 directive' was agreed
OL,12,Fby the park authority planning
OL,13,Fdepartment at a meeting on Wednesday,
OL,14,F22 January. This means that planning
OL,15,Fpermission is required from the
OL,16,Fauthority to convert a property into a
OL,17,Fsecond home or short-term holiday.
