OL,3,CNew rule approved to crack down on
OL,4,Csecond homes in national park
OL,6,FIn September 2024, the same directive
OL,7,Fwas issued by Cyngor Gwynedd for the
OL,8,Fwhole county, excluding the national
OL,9,Fpark. That decision was met with
OL,10,Fcriticism from some campaigners who
OL,11,Fargued the changes would reduce house
OL,12,Fprices and impact tourism.
OL,14,FThe decision by the Eryri National
OL,15,FPark Authority means from 1 June 2025,
OL,16,Fmore than 970 square miles of north
OL,17,FWales will fall under the rule.
