OL,3,CNew rule approved to crack down on
OL,4,Csecond homes in national park
OL,6,FIf you own a home, you have some basic
OL,7,Frights to make changes to it, these
OL,8,Fare called Permitted Development
OL,9,FRights.
OL,11,FUnder these rules, you can make
OL,12,Fchanges like building a small
OL,13,Fextension or making your home a shared
OL,14,Fhouse for up to six people without
OL,15,Fasking for planning permission.
OL,17,FIn Wales, second homes and holiday
OL,18,Fhomes have different classifications
OL,19,Ffrom regular residential homes:
