OL,3,CNew rule approved to crack down on
OL,4,Csecond homes in national park
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government brought in these
OL,7,Fclassifications to control the number
OL,8,Fof second homes in holiday hotspots.
OL,10,FArticle 4 is a planning rule that
OL,11,Flocal authorities can bring in to take
OL,12,Faway a particular permitted
OL,13,Fdevelopment right, in a particular
OL,14,Flocation. That means you would then
OL,15,Fhave to apply for planning permission.
