OL,4,Csecond homes in national park
OL,6,FThe Eryri National Park Authority
OL,7,Fchair said by implementing the policy,
OL,8,Fit "can begin to manage the number of
OL,9,Fresidential dwellings used for these
OL,10,Fpurposes in our communities, giving
OL,11,Flocal people an opportunity to live in
OL,12,Ftheir community".
